<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>142</hymn_number>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thihnak in a tho than cang, Ka Khamhtu Bawi Jesuh, Amah a nun kha ka
 hngalh, Zei bia hmanh chim hna seh, A dawtnak kut kha ka hmuh, A aw thlum
 kha ka theih, Ka herh lio caan kip ah ka pawngah a um.

[C1]
   A nung, A nung, Khrih Jesuh a nung ko, Kan i chok ti, Bia kan i
   ruah, Ka umnak kip ah khan, A nung, A nung, Khamhnak kha pek awkah, Ka
   hngalhnak na ka hal ahcun, Ka lung chungah a nung.

[V2]
 Ka pawng khuaza kip ah hin, A dawtnak kha ka hmuh, Ka lung re-thei
 hmanh seh law, Ka lung a dong lai lo, Lam a ka hmuhsak ka hngalh,
 Thlichia tho chungah khan, Amah a langh laini kha a phan cang lai.

[C2]
   A nung, A nung, Khrih Jesuh a nung ko, Kan i chok ti, Bia kan i
   ruah, Ka umnak kip ah khan, A nung, A nung, Khamhnak kha pek awkah, Ka
   hngalhnak na ka hal ahcun, Ka lung chungah a nung.

[V3]
 Lawm tuah, lawm tuah, Maw Khrihfa, Fakpi in thangthat tuah,
 Hal-le-lu-jah tiin, Jesuh Khrih Siangpahrang cu, A kawlmi vialte
 ruahchannak le, Bawmtu a si, Ahohmanh amah tluk tha cu an um lo.

[C3]
   A nung, A nung, Khrih Jesuh a nung ko, Kan i chok ti, Bia kan i
   ruah, Ka umnak kip ah khan, A nung, A nung, Khamhnak kha pek awkah, Ka
   hngalhnak na ka hal ahcun, Ka lung chungah a nung.</lyrics>
<title>A NUNG CH142</title>
</song>